(213,283,'Margetplace work','','<div class=\"marketplace-background\">\r\n<div class=\"container text-light\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col\">\r\n<div class=\"text-center pb-4\">\r\n<h2 class=\"font-header text-light mb-4\">How does the EnergySage<sup></sup> Marketplace work?</h2>\r\n<p class=\"wrap-description\">EnergySage connects you with vetted, local installers and providers who compete to earn your business. But we dont stop there. We help you easily and confidently switch to high-quality clean energy and energy-saving solutions by providing access to transparent information, unbiased advice, and a best-in-class shopping experience.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg text-center text-lg-left mb-4 mt-lg-5\">\r\n<h3 class=\"text-sans font-size-xl text-light text-uppercase\">Shoppers</h3>\r\n<p>Shop with confidence. Get the right solutions for you, your home, and your budget.</p>\r\n<hr class=\"line-bottom mr-lg-0\">\r\n<ul class=\"list-unstyled d-inline-block\">\r\n<li class=\"list-item mb-2 text-left d-flex flex-row align-items-center\"><img class=\"mr-2\" src=\"images/about-us/download.png\" width=\"25\" height=\"25\" loading=\"lazy\" data-path=\"local-images:/about-us/download.png\">Simplicity: Easily get quotes from multiple prescreened installers</li>\r\n<li class=\"list-item mb-2 text-left d-flex flex-row align-items-center\"><img class=\"mr-2\" src=\"images/about-us/download.png\" width=\"25\" height=\"25\" loading=\"lazy\" data-path=\"local-images:/about-us/download.png\">Savings: Access 20% lower prices (or more) vs. going it alone</li>\r\n<li class=\"list-item mb-2 text-left d-flex flex-row align-items-center\"><img class=\"mr-2\" src=\"images/about-us/download.png\" width=\"25\" height=\"25\" loading=\"lazy\" data-path=\"local-images:/about-us/download.png\">Trust: Transparency and objective advice with no pushy sales tactics</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg d-flex justify-content-center mb-5\">\r\n<div><img class=\"d-lg-block\" src=\"images/about-us/margetplace-lg.png\" width=\"323\" height=\"265\" loading=\"lazy\" data-path=\"local-images:/about-us/margetplace-lg.png\"> <img class=\"d-lg-none\" src=\"images/about-us/margetplace-sm.png\" width=\"266\" height=\"322\" loading=\"lazy\" data-path=\"local-images:/about-us/margetplace-sm.png\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg text-center text-lg-left mt-lg-5\">\r\n<div class=\"test\">\r\n<h3 class=\"text-sans font-size-xl text-light text-uppercase\">Installers &amp; manufacturers</h3>\r\n<p>EnergySage is a trusted partner for hundreds of clean energy companies and providers.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr class=\"line-bottom ml-lg-0\">\r\n<ul class=\"list-unstyled d-inline-block\">\r\n<li class=\"list-item mb-2 text-left d-flex flex-row align-items-center\"><img class=\"mr-2\" src=\"images/about-us/download.png\" width=\"25\" height=\"25\" loading=\"lazy\" data-path=\"local-images:/about-us/download.png\">Grow your business: Access to thousands of educated, highly-motivated shoppers</li>\r\n<li class=\"list-item mb-2 text-left d-flex flex-row align-items-center\"><img class=\"mr-2\" src=\"images/about-us/download.png\" width=\"25\" height=\"25\" loading=\"lazy\" data-path=\"local-images:/about-us/download.png\">Reduce your costs: Find and engage great customers faster and for less</li>\r\n<li class=\"list-item mb-2 text-left d-flex flex-row align-items-center\"><img class=\"mr-2\" src=\"images/about-us/download.png\" width=\"25\" height=\"25\" loading=\"lazy\" data-path=\"local-images:/about-us/download.png\">Simplify your sales: Quote, message, schedule, and sign  all from one platform</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>',1,'margetplace-work',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'mod_custom',1,1,'{\"prepare_content\":0,\"backgroundimage\":\"\",\"layout\":\"_:default\",\"moduleclass_sfx\":\"\",\"cache\":1,\"cache_time\":900,\"cachemode\":\"static\",\"module_tag\":\"div\",\"bootstrap_size\":\"0\",\"header_tag\":\"h3\",\"header_class\":\"\",\"style\":\"0\"}',0,'*'),
(214,284,'About Why trust us','','<div class=\"container my-5\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-10 offset-md-1 col-lg-8 offset-lg-2 text-center\">\r\n<h2>Why trust us?</h2>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.energysage.com/consumer-protection/\">Consumer protection</a> is at the heart of everything we do, from our deeply-researched guides to our transparent marketplace to our expert Energy Advisors. For more, read our <a href=\"https://www.energysage.com/editorial-guidelines/\">editorial guidelines</a>.</p>\r\n<p>The EnergySage Marketplace is a safe, no-commitment, no-pressure place to learn, shop, and compare.</p>\r\n<ol class=\"text-left\">\r\n<li class=\"mb-50\">Its completely free to submit your information and request quotes.</li>\r\n<li class=\"mb-50\">We protect all your contact information until you decide to share it with our installer network.</li>\r\n<li class=\"mb-50\">Youll only see quotes and offers from vetted providers.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>',1,'why-trust-us',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'mod_custom',1,1,'{\"prepare_content\":0,\"backgroundimage\":\"\",\"layout\":\"_:default\",\"moduleclass_sfx\":\"\",\"cache\":1,\"cache_time\":900,\"cachemode\":\"static\",\"module_tag\":\"div\",\"bootstrap_size\":\"0\",\"header_tag\":\"h3\",\"header_class\":\"\",\"style\":\"0\"}',0,'*'),
(215,285,'How our business works','','<div class=\"container mb-5\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg mb-4 text-center text-lg-left\"><img src=\"images/about-us/how-our-business.png\" width=\"507\" height=\"587\" loading=\"lazy\" data-path=\"local-images:/about-us/how-our-business.png\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg align-self-center text-center text-lg-left\">\r\n<h2 id=\"moneyDiagramLabel\" class=\"text-dark font-header mb-4\">How our business works</h2>\r\n<div id=\"moneyDiagramDetails\">\r\n<p>Installers and other service providers pay us a small fee to participate in our marketplace, but only after they are vetted for reliability and suitability to be part of the EnergySage platform. They cannot simply pay to be on our platform. They cannot bias our recommendation of their products or services.</p>\r\n<p>Our fee is a fraction of the cost these companies would otherwise spend on sales and marketing. When companies like these work directly with consumers, rather than through EnergySage, almost a quarter of the final price paid by the shopper goes towards covering such costs. EnergySage reduces these expenses for companies on our platform, allowing them to offer our shoppers far lower prices  usually, over 20% lower!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>',1,'how-our-business',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'mod_custom',1,1,'{\"prepare_content\":0,\"backgroundimage\":\"\",\"layout\":\"_:default\",\"moduleclass_sfx\":\"\",\"cache\":1,\"cache_time\":900,\"cachemode\":\"static\",\"module_tag\":\"div\",\"bootstrap_size\":\"0\",\"header_tag\":\"h3\",\"header_class\":\"\",\"style\":\"0\"}',0,'*'),
