(227,297,'About our team','','<div class=\"container\" data-v-13de8a37=\"\">\r\n<h1 class=\"text-gray-800 text-center mb-5\">Our Team</h1>\r\n<p class=\"text-center pb-4\">Click a team member below to learn more about them!</p>\r\n<div class=\"mx-auto card-flip-outer\">\r\n<div class=\"d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-start\">\r\n<div class=\"mx-2 card-flip\">\r\n<div class=\"card d-block position-relative border-0\">\r\n<div id=\"card-container-1\" class=\"cardImg d-block position-relative text-align-left\">\r\n<div class=\"description p-2 position-absolute\" style=\"display: none;\">\r\n<p>I was drawn to EnergySage because I was excited to work towards the common goal of making clean energy more accessible and transparent for consumers. Our team makes each day of work satisfying and fun! In my free time, you might find me reading, running, baking, or playing trumpet.</p>\r\n<p>Fun fact: I once walked a marathon without training.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<img class=\"image-hover\" src=\"images/about-us/careers/Emily_Ahuna.png\" width=\"255\" height=\"260\" loading=\"lazy\" data-path=\"local-images:/about-us/careers/Emily_Ahuna.png\"></div>\r\n<!-- Other card content -->\r\n<div class=\"d-flex\" data-v-792fcc06=\"\">\r\n<p class=\"mt-2 mb-0 text-headings font-size-lg text-gray-800 mr-auto\" data-v-792fcc06=\"\">Emily Ahuna</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"mb-0\" data-v-792fcc06=\"\">Software Engineer</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-gray-700\" data-v-792fcc06=\"\">She/her/hers</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"card d-block position-relative border-0\">\r\n<div id=\"card-container-1\" class=\"cardImg d-block position-relative text-align-left\">\r\n<div class=\"description p-2 position-absolute\" style=\"display: none;\">\r\n<p>I was drawn to EnergySage because I was excited to work towards the common goal of making clean energy more accessible and transparent for consumers. Our team makes each day of work satisfying and fun! In my free time, you might find me reading, running, bakin